<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
   <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-LN+7fdVzj6u52u30Kp6M/trliBMCMKTyK833zpbD+pXdCLuTusPj697FH4R/5mcr" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <title>FAQs - Sayan Blogs</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #e6f2ff, #ffffff);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .faq-section h2 {
      color: #007bff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .faq-item {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .question {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #0056b3;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .answer {
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

  <div class="container faq-section">
    <h2>FAQs</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="question">1. How do I create a blog post?</div>
      <div class="answer">Click on the "Create Post" button in the navigation bar. Fill out your title and content, then click "Publish".</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="question">2. Where can I view my submitted posts?</div>
      <div class="answer">Navigate to the "Posts" section from the top menu to see all the posts you've submitted.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="question">3. Can I edit or delete a blog once it is submitted?</div>
      <div class="answer">Currently, editing or deleting posts is not supported. Stay tuned for updates in future versions!</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="question">4. Who can see my posts?</div>
      <div class="answer">All posts are publicly visible on the "Posts" page of the blog site.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>

</body>
</html>
